{
 "name": "RPlog_Soft_Open",
 "title": "Soft Open",
 "summary": "The Caspian Presav Crestian Tarasar holds a soft opening for his new Prothium Club in Selene's Neon District, lending the venue to his friend Kipran Jawatha and Crown Princess Sonja Damion for a private party hosted by Grand Moff Elana Tracer. The young couple take to the dance floor as guests mingle, until the flamboyant IGN celebrity reporter Thurston Unger crashes the event with his camera crew, charming his way through introductions to Crestian, Tracer, and the shy Horansi diplomat Kasha Tabasuri. Thurston angles for future interviews -- bristling Crestian by addressing him as 'Mister' rather than by his titles -- and Kasha nervously agrees to speak about her people while being careful not to misrepresent them. As the young Moff Etiel te Danaan arrives to quietly court Tracer, Thurston wraps his rounds and departs for Republic space, leaving the relieved Kasha to retreat toward the buffet.",
